---
// src/components/GdelSystem.astro
---
<div class="system-card">
    <div class="icon">G</div>
    <div class="content">
        <h4>The Gdel System</h4>
        <p>
            An ancient pastoral practice of collective rangeland resting. Communities decide on exclusion periods to allow pastures to recover, adapting seasonal grazing patterns to climatic variability.
        </p>
    </div>
</div>

<style lang="scss">
    .system-card {
        display: flex;
        align-items: flex-start;
        gap: 1.5rem;
        background-color: var(--color-bg-alt);
        border-radius: 8px;
        padding: 1.5rem;
        margin: 2rem 0;
        border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    }
    .icon {
        flex-shrink: 0;
        width: 50px;
        height: 50px;
        border-radius: 50%;
        background-color: var(--color-primary);
        color: white;
        display: grid;
        place-content: center;
        font-family: var(--font-serif);
        font-size: 1.75rem;
        font-weight: 600;
    }
    h4 {
        font-family: var(--font-sans);
        font-size: 1.25rem;
        margin: 0 0 0.5rem 0;
        color: var(--color-primary);
    }
    p {
        font-family: var(--font-sans);
        font-size: 0.95rem;
        margin: 0;
        line-height: 1.6;
    }
</style>